author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be YouTube's moderation unfairly treating good content as if it's malicious. In the last few days many channels have received strikes and some have been completely terminated at the hands of a moderation bot that understands no context. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: YouTube Is Unfairly Shutting Down Tech Channels...
